---
---
<section id="projects" class="projects">
  <h2 class="section-title">Projects</h2>

  <article class="project">
    <div class="project-media">
      <img src="../../public/logo_bidle.png" alt="Bidle logo" />
    </div>
    <div class="project-body">
      <span class="tag">Personal project</span>
      <h3>Bidle</h3>
      <p>A mobile app built with React Native and a Python backend, using PostgreSQL for data storage. Private repository.</p>
      <div class="tech-tags">
        <span>React Native</span>
        <span>Python</span>
        <span>PostgreSQL</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="project reverse">
    <div class="project-media">
      <img src="../../public/logo_addee.png" alt="Addee logo" />
    </div>
    <div class="project-body">
      <span class="tag">Epitech Innovative Project — team of 5</span>
      <h3>Addee</h3>
      <p>A gamified prevention and community app built as part of Epitech's Innovative Project. Confidential — demo available on request.</p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <div class="experience">
    <h2 class="section-title">Professional experience</h2>
    <div class="timeline">

      <article class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-date">Apr — Jul 2026</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-header">
            <h3>Enterprise analytics platform</h3>
            <span class="confidential-badge">🔒 Confidential</span>
          </div>
          <p>Designed a company-wide KPI dashboard on Microsoft Fabric: mapped internal data sources, defined around 40 KPIs with business stakeholders, built semantic models and set up the underlying Azure infrastructure.</p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span>Microsoft Fabric</span>
            <span>Power BI</span>
            <span>Azure</span>
            <span>DAX</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-date">Apr — Jul 2026</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-header">
            <h3>IT operational dashboard</h3>
            <span class="confidential-badge">🔒 Confidential</span>
          </div>
          <p>Built two Power BI dashboards on IT ticketing activity, working from a database of over 1,200 tables narrowed to a clean core of 12. Wrote custom DAX measures for resolution time (business hours only) and first-contact resolution rate.</p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span>Power BI</span>
            <span>DAX</span>
            <span>SQL</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-date">Apr — Jul 2026</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-header">
            <h3>Streaming analytics project</h3>
            <span class="confidential-badge">🔒 Confidential</span>
          </div>
          <p>Designed an automated reporting solution for a video platform subsidiary, replacing a manual, error-prone spreadsheet process. Defined KPIs and client segmentation, and built a prototype dashboard on simulated data.</p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span>Power BI</span>
            <span>Microsoft Fabric</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-date">Jul — Dec 2024</div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-header">
            <h3>Network storage billing report</h3>
            <span class="confidential-badge">🔒 Confidential</span>
          </div>
          <p>Built a Python ETL pipeline to automate a billing report, with CRUD integration into the internal portal and monthly automation via Airflow.</p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span>Python</span>
            <span>PostgreSQL</span>
            <span>Airflow</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .projects {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .project {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .project.reverse {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 200px;
  }
  .project.reverse .project-media {
    order: 2;
  }
  .project-media img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .project-body h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0.4rem 0 0.6rem;
  }
  .project-body p {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
  }
  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .tech-tags span {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    background: var(--accent-light);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 3px 9px;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .experience {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 130px 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .timeline-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .timeline-date {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-top: 0.15rem;
  }
  .timeline-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .timeline-header h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .confidential-badge {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2px 10px;
  }
  .timeline-content p {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .project, .project.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .project.reverse .project-media {
      order: 0;
    }
    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
